title: Spygate Erupts! (Ep 1705)
description:
In this episode I address the explosion of new information that came out in the Spygate case. 

News Picks:


Here’s what really happened in the spying scandal on the Trump campaign.

Banks are now freezing monies going to political causes they don’t like.

This is dystopia, disguised as democracy.
